 we conclude that the\nelectron density in the ionized layer associated with the ionization front is\nof order 10^4 cm^-3. Finally, our analysis of the helium and hydrogen\nrecombination lines implies essential coincidence of the helium and hydrogen\nStromgren spheres.\n","versions":[{"version":"v1","created":"Sat, 4 Oct 1997 20:59:01 GMT"}],"update_date":"2007-05-23"}
