chanism functioning in a zone of radiation\nflux gradient. The effects of nonlocal convection and the dynamic coupling\nbetween convection and oscillations are discussed. The spatial oscillations of\nthe thermal variables in the pulsational calculations have been effectively\nsuppressed.\n","versions":[{"version":"v1","created":"Sun, 5 Oct 1997 08:01:03 GMT"}],"update_date":"2009-10-30"}
